arrayGenerator

Interface ListingGenerator

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ArrayGenerator
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CleverRandomListingGenerator, CleverRandomListingGeneratorTimer, RandomListingGenerator, SimpleRandomListingGenerator, SimpleRandomListingGeneratorTimer, SortedListingGenerator

    public interface ListingGenerator
extends ArrayGenerator
    A Listing is a special type of Array, in which an array of size n will contain each of the values 0..n-1 exactly once. See the corresponding tester class, which defines a method to test whether a listing has this property.
    Version:
    September 2020
    Author:
    Hugh Osborne
